data.title: Hot Wheels The Super Mario Bros. Movie Jungle Kingdom Raceway
meta_keywords: Hot Wheels The Super Mario Bros. Movie Jungle Kingdom Raceway
data.meta_description: Shop Hot Wheels The Super Mario Bros. Movie Jungle Kingdom Raceway at Target. Choose from Same Day Delivery, Drive Up or Order Pickup. Free standard shipping with $35 orders.
data.text: Hot Wheels The Super Mario Bros. Movie Jungle Kingdom playset and vehicle take the onscreen action offscreen! Inspired by Nintendo + Illumination’s The Super Mario Bros. Movie, this track set features a wild ride to challenge players and bring a rush of thrills -- there’s a waterfall jump, a broken loop and some tight turns to navigate. Those who make it through complete the loop to go again. Kids just slam the launcher to start the action. One Mario 1:64 scale die-cast car is included for play right out of the box! The set makes a great gift for kids ages 5 years and older who love racing and stunting, especially Super Mario fans. Colors and decorations may vary.
